<note n="0339001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0339001">Padumukkhcpa-Vagga 所謂向空中投最上水草即鉢頭摩花故，品名從而名為「蓮花投」。</note>
<note n="0339002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0339002">Atalikkhacara（空中行）。</note>
<note n="0340001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0340001">Succhavi（美膚）。</note>
<note n="0340001-1" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0340001-1">參閱第二三五之第一偈。</note>
<note n="0340002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0340002">aḍḍhacanda（半月）未詳，應為花名。</note>
<note n="0341003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0341003">Devapa（天飲）。</note>
<note n="0341001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0341001">Samantacakkhu（徧眼）。</note>
<note n="0344001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0344001">如暹羅本讀為 heṭṭhāsiso。</note>
<note n="0346001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0346001">Upāgatabhāsaniya 長老昔日曾為羅剎，依此故有如斯稱謂。</note>
</p>
